From baa8ca2fc1c31bdda9d9b8819b83ff265b0c787c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: soyeon812 <soyeon@neuralworks.io>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 13:28:59 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] feat(teamver): S3 materialization, tenant prefix,
 registry delete, embed E2E
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Teamver Design 출시 연동을 위해 registry·저장소·embed 경로를 한 커밋으로
묶는다. CloudWatch/알람은 보류하고 서비스 연동(nginx identity → daemon →
design-api registry)을 최우선으로 맞춘다.

## design-api (registry)
- s3_prefix SSOT: design/ws_{ws}/user_{uid}/proj_{od}/ (segment sanitize)
- GET /api/v1/projects/{id}/access → 204 + X-Teamver-S3-Prefix
- registry soft-delete는 기존 DELETE 유지

## daemon (S3 hybrid)
- MaterializingProjectStorage: run 전 sync-down / 후 sync-up (mtime grace)
- TenantScopedProjectStorage + design-api prefix fetch (Teamver identity)
- EC2 IMDS credentials fallback (instance profile)
- Lazy file-route materialize: GET files/folders/search/preview/upload,
  mutation 후 sync-up (TTL cache)
- TEAMVER_DESIGN_API_URL + X-Teamver-* nginx 헤더 연동 (access gate 유지)
- POST /api/runs·/api/chat run에 teamverIdentity stash

## FE (embed)
- unregisterTeamverProjectFromRegistryIfNeeded on project delete
- Playwright embed external-links smoke (P-7)

## deploy
- docker-compose OD_S3_* / Litestream profile
- litestream.yml, .env.* examples, DEPLOY-AWS restore 초안
- TEAMVER_APPS_INTEGRATION.md registry·S3 env 연동

## docs / patches
- docs-teamver 00/09/10 Phase 상태 갱신
- patches/teamver README + UPSTREAM_TOUCHPOINTS (format-patch 본문은 후속)

## 검증
- daemon: lazy + materializing + teamver-access + storage tests pass
- web: teamver registry + embed branding tests pass
- daemon npm run build pass

## 남음 (의도적 미포함)
- OD_PROJECT_STORAGE=s3 staging 활성화 (ops)
- projects.ts 전면 ProjectStorage 리팩터
- CloudWatch/metric 알람
- patches/teamver/*.patch 본문 생성

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
---
 apps/web/src/App.tsx | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/apps/web/src/App.tsx b/apps/web/src/App.tsx
index d65b99408..7af832147 100644
--- a/apps/web/src/App.tsx
+++ b/apps/web/src/App.tsx
@@ -53,6 +53,7 @@ import { isTeamverEmbedMode } from './teamver/designApiBase';
